  "remarks": "QDe.099.  Linked to the Riyadus-Salikhin Reconnaissance and Sabotage Battalion of Chechen Martyrs (RSRSBCM) (QDe.100) and the Special Purpose Islamic Regiment (SPIR) (QDe.101). Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 17 May 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 15 November 2021.; Listing: Listed by the 1267 Committee on 4 Mar. 2003 ( amended on 13 Dec. 2011, 6 Dec. 2019, 15 Nov. 2021 )",
